  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "XkjmO8GZw+NPlqtsKIz94hXoCCSSximfmFKrLHYsZ2I=",
    "originContent": "## Motivation",
    "translatedContent": "## 动机"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "S/FmevxxOq1wYir+ajbWgUA8OmYhFjEB281m7DHQSZU=",
    "originContent": "Animation graphs are an essential tool for managing the complexity present in",
    "translatedContent": "动画图是管理现代3D游戏动画流程复杂性的关键工具。当您的游戏拥有数十个"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "ODutFojpeaPxD1bBgXFe/kAZJo4HW2Qi2MdhPsdcZLI=",
    "originContent": "the animation pipelines for modern 3D games. When your game has tens of",
    "translatedContent": "动画，且包含复杂的混合和过渡，或者您想通过极少的关键帧程序化生成动画时，"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "7pDknpVnL5dHDvFUX8HVav1INaEl6MaKHqed3gZbSdc=",
    "originContent": "animations with complex blends and transitions, or you want to generate your",
    "translatedContent": "简单的动画剪辑播放就远远不够了。"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "LJuuJgRGWTGp+LWEHFpWYCuL+LwI9BqhUknITVHR7e0=",
    "originContent": "animations procedurally from very few keyframes, simple animation clip playback",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "LfvhhOacy0Ns4WQaYrqTzD0SR/o/8FnQOXWBqSPnin0=",
    "originContent": "is not enough.",
    "translatedContent": "该 crate 作为大多数 `bevy_animation` 的替代方案，旨在"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "提供完整的动画系统和开发工作流程，包括动画图、动画状态机（即动画控制器）"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "f8/XZP+bL1aE8su10ZVSH5cYi1UQj6U5iwNk1z/p2rI=",
    "originContent": "This crate works as an alternative to most of `bevy_animation`, and aims to",
    "translatedContent": "以及用于创建动画图和状态机的图形编辑器。"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "Gf3YjGNVaDuPKyNHAUFzablqZjkQYJ88pKrd/T/aBNw=",
    "originContent": "provide a complete animation system and development workflow including animation",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "DvepCfOHlnJe1+xyqtwMVaLqrwIwtBsU3caHw82XX/U=",
    "originContent": "graphs, animation state machines (i.e. animation controllers) and a graphical",
    "translatedContent": "_注意：此项目与 `bevy_animation` 0.14 版本中引入的动画图是分开的。_"
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "HejRfeNTYnyepV0yLN4Hq3RhUZqRrgRMprGlEWctAwQ=",
    "originContent": "editor to create your animation graphs and state machines.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "![示例使用截图](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mbrea-c/bevy_animation_graph/master/locomotion_graph.png)"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "r4N0Wy2njR9x1ksaNzykUbdpmGtab9FLPOC1vm/Dl+0=",
    "originContent": "_NOTE: This project is separate from the animation graphs introduced in",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "hh0kzZRd6K3a2Nihl6jancQLKaETM+98YsFoif1ydPg=",
    "originContent": "`bevy_animation` in version 0.14._",
    "translatedContent": "## 当前功能"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "LhTY8eSBTWfFcPVov9zm/hEMpN2efCMeR80m56hPM90=",
    "originContent": "![example usage screenshot](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mbrea-c/bevy_animation_graph/master/locomotion_graph.png)",
    "translatedContent": "- 动画图是资源。它们可以从资源文件加载，也可以通过符合人体工学的 API 在代码中创建。"
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- 可视化图形编辑器。"
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "VsOY7dxcNnT8chph5ZIzmj7+smEcdlA3XrYDXMgVaUU=",
    "originContent": "## Current Features",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "6elyRWlRkCKgViw2rjjMwZ85+E59cCbqcir1PDKyM9E=",
    "originContent": "- Animation graphs are assets. They can be loaded from asset files, or created",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "HY9gmzHkWjYLT6p0Xkn7PJkdwy7q9PmamTq5qjsSTF4=",
    "originContent": "  in code with an ergonomic API.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "QiOmSNgBL1UwGYSF+htO/EH3lSUdjLB1SSPfoVT9HkQ=",
    "originContent": "- Visual graph editor.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "inj1lby+yUIMQ28kELZY+nzxkpwr/yX/78TcVKzW3u4=",
    "originContent": "- Animation state machines:",
    "translatedContent": "- 动画状态机："
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "W8xhXbA3N1iKUqmdLFLxhvrz5BBNh0N/FSihdoLM43o=",
    "originContent": "  - Animation state machines are embedded as nodes in animation graphs.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 动画状态机作为节点嵌入动画图中。"
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "NQz6+v+y0ILQ+zlXxCUw7b3z/gA3pydMLGRF9ItqJQ4=",
    "originContent": "  - Each state in a state machines plays back its own animation graph on demand.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 状态机中的每个状态按需播放其自身的动画图。"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "awHZbKfcd1K9ZbQittCdqINVqriDnhVhC0dcV/zZEzU=",
    "originContent": "  - Transitions also have their own animation graph, and they can query source",
    "translatedContent": "  - 转换也有自己的动画图，并且可以查询源状态和目标状态的动画图。"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "H0qPAUaSIwSWcnFnBNdtYXkHK/S9adqQzrAOiGxm3KQ=",
    "originContent": "    and target states' animation graphs.",
    "translatedContent": "- 布娃娃支持："
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "OIOfnKaQgyzs0+Mnhfd1qpqHtjpeJY0cnP/riO96jrw=",
    "originContent": "- Ragdoll support:",
    "translatedContent": "  - 编辑器中可视化布娃娃编辑。"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "AOf0RPnnqN1ypmN+8AJiJ7nQDOWAbhC/QV7QYAWfwrI=",
    "originContent": "  - Visual ragdoll editing in the editor.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 支持_部分布娃娃_，其中部分骨骼通过物理模拟，其他骨骼由目标动画姿势驱动。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "XsMaDalCkY3XDnMOUUcNoggyMXqMwpt6dFsSsKJaND8=",
    "originContent": "  - Support for _partial ragdolls_, where some bones are simulated and others",
    "translatedContent": "- 支持用 Rust 编写自定义节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "7hgwawS5zw31MvwVw/tfUlkGTItRvjwo9+fb8A8k8tw=",
    "originContent": "    kinematically driven by a target animation pose.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 用户可以通过添加编辑器插件并在 Bevy 类型注册表中注册额外的自定义节点来创建自己的编辑器二进制文件。"
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "ihoU/z+Jq2pzAjWWc1AaBDcGhIbnWYlaUxup8MCIlcA=",
    "originContent": "- Support for custom nodes written in Rust.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 编辑器会自动识别所有已注册的节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "VR7KqtqXkE4QR4aC2xXim4H4In4SDsCh8T4JVySeTXE=",
    "originContent": "  - Users can create their own editor binary by adding the editor plugin and",
    "translatedContent": "- 内置节点包括："
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "3M+agQC4m+yuh5adKmuEMpTTwjSr69/GTQbJgH+ZNnw=",
    "originContent": "    registering their additional custom nodes in the Bevy type registry. The",
    "translatedContent": "  - 动画链式播放（即一个节点接着另一个播放）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "a46YSxg1l7Pp93sgGUN1q+KVCtfXOUiZI1gOcxg487w=",
    "originContent": "    editor will automatically pick up all registered nodes.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 两骨反向运动学。"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "I7i/OiGfnjG8FtAenaNfKG0Y3JFxrOLJHYyz20do+h4=",
    "originContent": "- Available built-in nodes include:",
    "translatedContent": "  - 循环播放。"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "6xA9SUpUq/Xdvk9KYYxhKgU8yYFDaVmZVpkZVcL2Kl4=",
    "originContent": "  - Animation chaining (i.e. play one node after another).",
    "translatedContent": "  - 线性混合（在骨骼空间中）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "xvrG4Ip9DLtgto3Qi4iYfpK5eYwHZ3Er7nO3lWnhhMw=",
    "originContent": "  - Two-bone inverse kinematics.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 2D 混合空间节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "tvp46zPtUq7m/6A6xcIaQocfHnL6LdHyu9+3YUsr91c=",
    "originContent": "  - Looping.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 关于 YZ 平面的动画镜像。"
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "pJfLwGWETShrEWhjalQE9FYkgqSVBtjSyP3XW2r7oFI=",
    "originContent": "  - Linear Blending (in bone space).",
    "translatedContent": "  - 动画剪辑播放。"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "+lhKapB+QHTZsdKcH/xcHC/Xhgzf8Dqr/35JCIV7bOE=",
    "originContent": "  - 2D Blend space node.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 使用骨骼蒙版对某些骨骼应用给定的旋转。"
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "NWp6Oe/qVfRFktepwInk+osvVjqST/0GVAFkscbsxrE=",
    "originContent": "  - Mirror animation about the YZ plane.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 加速或减慢动画播放速度。"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "3fqOdZ+6y9ggWkUIEYuyqCZ/8iB2xsAswtF9zr1TZnk=",
    "originContent": "  - Animation clip playback.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 动画图节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "3uBWenEDRyP28OCwr84+WGpHXBICX8gmUvuuRkAidL4=",
    "originContent": "  - Apply a given rotation to some bones in a pose using a bone mask.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 动画状态机节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "/MmGt00ruFb3SBSkbSn35uGtVl7D0aOtIblztSHdU80=",
    "originContent": "  - Speed up or slow down animation playback.",
    "translatedContent": "  - 算术节点：对 f32、Vec3、Quat 等常见操作的多种支持。"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "607NDqRXBkMUdcqkbcOZD/vNZWjl3tSKdL0/ntNb8Zc=",
    "originContent": "  - Animation graph node.",
    "translatedContent": "- 嵌套动画图作为其他动画图中的节点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "yIk9p9+rsqyeV4eQka6Ej2HuASqR4hfJu5sWO/ijpr0=",
    "originContent": "  - Animation state machine node.",
    "translatedContent": "- 使用事件轨道进行动画同步。"
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "LvgOkFz/JDHPAOPDJTzWQpMZf1Z6jKveJzYLZMwUVj8=",
    "originContent": "  - Arithmetic nodes: a variety of common operations on f32, Vec3, Quat, etc.",
    "translatedContent": "- 节点输出进行缓存以避免不必要的计算。"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "lPhBixoc8/fsb55QNo9/UKS1bQC28B7Gkvb6fy2sNts=",
    "originContent": "- Nesting animation graphs as nodes within other graphs.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "OAO5AVKV7DAK0nlLYGkjRQW7lhoWTYG3WHwpA3qmr1o=",
    "originContent": "- Animation synchronization using event tracks.",
    "translatedContent": "## 计划功能"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "dyJV5neQxiPyiP6jFtmTIUDlQZmHgRe08APsEPp4SV4=",
    "originContent": "- Output from graph nodes is cached to avoid unnecessary computations.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "1. 布娃娃“姿势跟随”模式，模拟布娃娃骨骼尝试通过物理力匹配目标姿势："
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "m8VYPv6MlPmvDAxmcWcJghJATdr9ezmdfLEXGpbdA/E=",
    "originContent": "## Planned Features",
    "translatedContent": "   - _绝对_匹配模式，跟踪目标骨骼的世界空间位置/旋转，并作为弹簧力作用于布娃娃骨骼的锚点。"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "   - _相对_匹配模式，布娃娃骨骼尝试匹配相对于其父骨骼的目标位置/旋转。我们可能需要 Avian 支持关节马达以正确实现此模式。"
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "4UibTFrhTMDzIQMaDGjV4zR8EASk4jYmM6+NXfhVc9M=",
    "originContent": "1. Ragdoll \"pose following\" modes, where a simulated ragdoll bones try to match",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "FU5lGAw7wSOVCX1boFue4QpIkuo3IBNtAKHqgpuiHk0=",
    "originContent": "   a target pose using physical forces:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "1oJoE30X6aMCS74bBWXkcy5Obw6qqdBwRKLS5YPceuk=",
    "originContent": "   - _Absolute_ matching mode, where the world space position/rotation of the",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
